ENL Commercial Mauritius Rises to 1-Month High as Profit Triples

-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 
2011-10-03T09:46:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/enl-commercial-mauritius-rises-to-1-month-high-as-profit-triples.html
ENL Commercial Ltd. (GIDC) , a Mauritian
company with interests in motor dealership and manufacturing,
rose to the highest in a month after saying profit more than
tripled in the year through June.  The stock gained 0.2 rupee, or 0.8 percent, to 26.20 rupees
by the 1:30 p.m. close in  Port Louis , the capital, the strongest
closing level since Sept. 1  Net income increased to 85 million rupees ($3 million) from
26.6 million rupees a year earlier, ENL Commercial said in a
 statement  published today on the Stock Exchange of Mauritiusâ€™s
